CHAT.comment: Teaching , Mother and Child sit on living room floor. Mother first teaches Child to string beads on a shoelace. Then she tries to teach Child to put black and white beads in separate piles. Child is not very cooperative. Her speech is fairly easy to understand.

u.a: Tries to string beads on wrong end of string .
picks up other end of string .
tries task on correct end of string .
reaches for Child's hand with bead .
gives string and bead to Child .
starts putting all the buttons in box .
tries to take button from Child .
